org.treetank.node.delegates

Class StructNodeDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.treetank.node.delegates.StructNodeDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INode, IStructNode

    public class StructNodeDelegate
extends Object
implements IStructNode
    Delegate method for all nodes building up the structure. That means that all nodes representing trees in Treetank are represented by an instance of the interface IStructNode namely containing the position of all related siblings, the first-child and all nodes defined by the NodeDelegate as well.
    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
